Ideas on this game

Inspiration:
	Taking elements from Flagship (a fps space rts game)
	
	Incoroporate mechanics of Star Citizen and Elite (fps control and flight mechanic)
	
	Allow for Strategic play amongst multiplay players, promotes teamwork and camadarie

	


Focus primarily on Skirmishes between 2-4 faction (developement come later)
Hopes to implement a Campaign as a multiplayer thing for exclusive prizes and accolade and general fun